为了避免使用 `while` 循环，并直接计算出应该移除的元素数量，我们可以先计算出需要达到的上信号占总数的比例，之后根据这个比例找出需要移除的 `KNodeTrain` 元素数量。下面是对应的代码实现：

```java
@Override
public List<KNodeTrain> kNodeTrainsPostProcess(@NotNull List<KNodeTrain> kNodeTrains, @NotNull ServiceWrapper serviceWrapper) {
    kNodeTrains = kNodeTrains.parallelStream().filter(kNodeTrain -> !kNodeTrain.isReset()).collect(Collectors.toList());
    var param = serviceWrapper.getParamObj(TrainDataUpSignalBalanceParam.class);
    int up = kNodeTrains.parallelStream().mapToInt(KNodeTrain::upSignal).sum();

    int targetCount = (int) ((1 - param.getThreshold()) * kNodeTrains.size());
    if (up < targetCount) {
        List<KNodeTrain> sorted = kNodeTrains.stream()
                .filter(kNodeTrain -> !kNodeTrain.isUp())
                .sorted(Comparator.comparing(kNodeTrain -> Math.abs(kNodeTrain.getFuturePercent())))
                .collect(Collectors.toList());
        int toRemoveCount = up - targetCount;
        kNodeTrains.removeAll(sorted.subList(0, Math.min(sorted.size(), toRemoveCount)));
    } else if (up > targetCount) {
        List<KNodeTrain> sorted = kNodeTrains.stream()
                .filter(KNodeTrain::isUp)
                .sorted(Comparator.comparing(kNodeTrain -> Math.abs(kNodeTrain.getFuturePercent())))
                .collect(Collectors.toList());
        int toRemoveCount = up - targetCount;
        kNodeTrains.removeAll(sorted.subList(0, Math.min(sorted.size(), toRemoveCount)));
    }

    return kNodeTrains;
}
```

